column2: Bitcoin is enjoying a great rally but its technology can't do even half of what "blockchain" enthusiasts espouse. Hence Ethereum; like both.
I'm happy to continue supporting Ethereum if it means upsetting Bitcoin maximalists. Congrats on your (our) success. More than 1 blockchain
